OL,7,FThe mother and girlfriend of a man
OL,8,Fconvicted of abusing his partner Kiena
OL,9,FDawes before she took her own life,
OL,10,Fare both under police investigation
OL,11,Ffor allegedly "coaching" him to give
OL,12,Fevidence.
OL,14,FRyan Wellings, 30, made a number of
OL,15,F"calls" to his mother, Lisa Green, and
OL,16,Fcurrent girlfriend, Emma Croft, who
OL,17,Fhad both attended the trial to support
OL,18,FWellings from the public gallery,
OL,19,Fspeaking about his evidence.
