OL,3,CMother and girlfriend of abuser
OL,4,Cinvestigated for alleged evidence
OL,5,C'coaching'
OL,7,FWellings, being held at HMP Preston,
OL,8,Fwas in the middle of giving evidence
OL,9,Fand, while entitled to speak to family
OL,10,Fand friends, he was not legally
OL,11,Fallowed to discuss his case with them.
OL,13,FBut the prosecution were made aware of
OL,14,Fthe calls, and, before the jury was
OL,15,Fbrought back into court following the
OL,16,FChristmas break, Paul Greaney KC,
OL,17,Fprosecuting, told the judge there had
OL,18,Fbeen "developments".
