OL,7,FBut if Wellings' defence wanted to
OL,8,Fcall the defendant's mother or
OL,9,Fgirlfriend to give evidence for him,
OL,10,Fthen Mr Greaney said he would be
OL,11,Fentitled to ask them to account for
OL,12,Ftheir actions.
OL,14,FNeither were called as defence
OL,15,Fwitnesses during the six-week trial.
