OL,7,FThe judge, Honorary Recorder of
OL,8,FPreston Robert Altham, said: "At the
OL,9,Fmoment, there's a prima facie that
OL,10,Fthere's been discussion between the
OL,11,Fdefendant and Emma Croft and Lisa
OL,12,FGreen, which may have been improper."
OL,14,FJudge Altham banned both from entering
OL,15,Fcourt until verdicts were returned and
OL,16,Fonly if they agreed to hand over their
OL,17,Fphones.
